connect

public TrackerWebServicesClient connect(java.lang.String systemId,
                                        java.lang.String systemKind,
                                        java.lang.String repositoryId,
                                        java.lang.String repositoryKind,
                                        java.lang.String connectionInfo,
                                        java.lang.String credentialInfo)
                                 throws MaxConnectionsReachedException,
                                        ConnectionException
Connects to the source SFEE system using the connectionInfo and credentialInfo details. This method uses the ConnectionManager configured in the wiring file for the SFEEReader

Parameters:
systemId - - The system id of the source SFEE system
systemKind - - The system kind of the source SFEE system
repositoryId - - The tracker id in the source SFEE system
repositoryKind - - The repository kind for the tracker
connectionInfo - - The SFEE server URL
credentialInfo - - User name and password concatenated with a delimiter.
Returns:
- The connection object obtained from the ConnectionManager
Throws:
MaxConnectionsReachedException
ConnectionException
